(4, 'Dayara Bugyal', 'Uttarakhand', 'Easy', '12058', 8, 6, 'Dayara Bugyal has all the elements of a perfect Himalayan trek: superb forests, beautiful campsites, ancient villages, thrilling climbs to high points, wonderful mountain views and few of the best alpine meadows of Uttarakhand. All of this in an easy-moderate trek  a gift we rarely see.\r\n\r\nDayara Bugyal has all the elements of a perfect Himalayan trek: superb forests, beautiful campsites, ancient villages, thrilling climbs to high points, wonderful mountain views and few of the best alpine meadows of Uttarakhand. All of this in an easy-moderate trek  a gift we rarely see.\r\n\r\nDayara Bugyal has all the elements of a perfect Himalayan trek: superb forests, beautiful campsites, ancient villages, thrilling climbs to high points, wonderful mountain views and few of the best alpine meadows of Uttarakhand. All of this in an easy-moderate trek  a gift we rarely see.\r\n\r\nDayara Bugyal has all the elements of a perfect Himalayan trek: superb forests, beautiful campsites, ancient villages, thrilling climbs to high points, wonderful mountain views and few of the best alpine meadows of Uttarakhand. All of this in an easy-moderate trek  a gift we rarely see.\r\n\r\nDayara Bugyal has all the elements of a perfect Himalayan trek: superb forests, beautiful campsites, ancient villages, thrilling climbs to high points, wonderful mountain views and few of the best alpine meadows of Uttarakhand. All of this in an easy-moderate trek  a gift we rarely see.\r\n\r\n\r\n', 9000, 'https://images.thrillophilia.com/image/upload/s--njOAV-bJ--/c_fill,f_auto,fl_strip_profile,h_600,q_auto,w_975/v1/images/photos/000/026/984/original/Dayara-Bugyal-Trek_2.jpg.jpg?1453310753', 'http://dmgupcwbwy0wl.cloudfront.net/system/images/000/108/059/3a79e4b84beeca129f1e91d80271505d/original/Dayara_Bugyal_Trek_BEDINI_1440x640.jpg?1555070051', 'https://indiahikes.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Dayara-Bugyal-trek-Indiahikes-Sudheer-Hegde-Trek-Lead