(7, 'Sandakphu', 'Nepal', 'Moderate', '11973', 18, 9, 'Sandakphu, being the highest peak in West Bengal, offers grand views of the worlds tallest peaks. Lhotse and Makalu, the fourth and fifth highest peaks in the world stand tall at 8,516m and 8,463m, trying to outdo the worlds tallest peak. But how can they? After all, the Everest stands between them, towering over everything!\r\n\r\nSandakphu, being the highest peak in West Bengal, offers grand views of the worlds tallest peaks. Lhotse and Makalu, the fourth and fifth highest peaks in the world stand tall at 8,516m and 8,463m, trying to outdo the worlds tallest peak. But how can they? After all, the Everest stands between them, towering over everything!\r\n\r\nSandakphu, being the highest peak in West Bengal, offers grand views of the worlds tallest peaks. Lhotse and Makalu, the fourth and fifth highest peaks in the world stand tall at 8,516m and 8,463m, trying to outdo the worlds tallest peak. But how can they? After all, the Everest stands between them, towering over everything!\r\n\r\nSandakphu, being the highest peak in West Bengal, offers grand views of the worlds tallest peaks. Lhotse and Makalu, the fourth and fifth highest peaks in the world stand tall at 8,516m and 8,463m, trying to outdo the worlds tallest peak. But how can they? After all, the Everest stands between them, towering over everything!\r\n\r\n', 13500, 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/b9gA962Ba6s/maxresdefault.jpg', 'https://indiahikes.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Sandakphu-snow-indiahikes.jpg', 'https://images.thrillophilia.com/image/upload/s--CzNayH3c--/c_fill,f_auto,fl_strip_profile,h_600,q_auto,w_975/v1/images/photos/000/074/252/original/sandakphu_phalut_1.jpg.jpg?1461318713', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/88/Sandakphu.jpg', 'data:image/jpeg;base64,', '2019-11-08', 'Bagdogra Airport', '8452055724', 1),
